  <text>
    <front>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p1">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l1"/>
          <choice>
                        <abbr>Sig.</abbr>
                        <expan>Signore (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice>
          <choice>
                        <abbr>Cons.</abbr>
                        <expan>Consigliere (Ratsmitglied)</expan>
                    </choice> Alfredo Escher <lb xml:id="p1-l2"/>
                    <placeName type="place" key="Zürich (Stadt)">Zurigo</placeName>.</p>
      </div>
      <div type="dateline">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p2">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l3"/>
          <placeName type="place" key="Lugano">Lugano</placeName>
          <date when="1868-05-25">25 Maggio 1868</date>.</p>
      </div>
    </front>
    <body>
            <div>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p3">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l4"/>Sino dal primo suscitarsi qui il progetto di chiedere
				<lb xml:id="p1-l5"/>una concessione del tronco di ferrovia <placeName type="place" key="Chiasso">Chiasso</placeName> –
				<lb xml:id="p1-l6"/>
                <hi rend="underline">
                    <placeName type="place" key="Lugano">Lugano</placeName>
                </hi>, verbo scritto ai <choice>
                        <abbr>sig<hi rend="sup">ri</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>signori (Herren)</expan>
                    </choice> <persName type="person" key="Zingg Josef">Zingg</persName> e
				<lb xml:id="p1-l7"/>
                <persName type="person" key="Koller Gottlieb">Koller-Burckardt</persName>
                <note type="transcript">sic!</note>, informandoli del fatto, e
				<lb xml:id="p1-l8"/>per averne instruzioni.
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p4">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l9"/>Non avendone avuto risposto, credo conveniente
				<lb xml:id="p1-l10"/>di mandare ai medesimi ed a Lei, <choice>
                        <abbr>Preg<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Pregiatissimo (Verehrtester)</expan>
                    </choice> <lb xml:id="p1-l11"/>
                <choice>
                        <abbr>Sig.</abbr>
                        <expan>Signore (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice> Consigliere, copie del Capitolato, che
				<lb xml:id="p1-l12"/>comprende anche la concessione del tronco
				<lb xml:id="p1-l13"/>
                <placeName type="place" key="Locarno">Locarno</placeName>–<placeName type="place" key="Biasca">Biasca</placeName>,
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p5">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l14"/>Se mai, nell'interesse dello scopo che si è prefisso
				<lb xml:id="p1-l15"/>il comitato del <placeName type="place" key="St. Gotthard (Pass)">Gottardo</placeName>, occorressero ulteriori
				<lb xml:id="p1-l16"/>informazioni od atti, mi troverò pronti ai
				<lb xml:id="p1-l17"/>suoi ordini.
			</p>
      <p rend="left" xml:id="K_6656_p6">
                <lb xml:id="p1-l18"/>Accolga, <choice>
                        <abbr>Preg<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Pregiatissimo (Verehrtester)</expan>
                    </choice> <choice>
                        <abbr>Sig<hi rend="sup">re</hi>
                </abbr>
                        <expan>Signore (Herr)</expan>
                    </choice>, l'espressione di tutta la mia
				<lb xml:id="p1-l19"/>considerazione,
			</p>
    </div>
        </body>
    <back>
      <div type="closer">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p7">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l20"/>
          <choice>
                        <abbr>Dev<hi rend="sup">mo</hi> </abbr>
                        <expan>Devotissimo (ergebenst)</expan>
                    </choice> servo
			</p>
      </div>
      <div type="address">
        <p rend="right" xml:id="K_6656_p8">
                    <lb xml:id="p1-l21"/>Pasquale Veladini</p>
      </div>
    </back>
